column2: SELECT t.thingid, t.ndetect,t.ra,t.dec,d.objid,p.mjd,p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.err_u,p.err_g,p.err_r,p.err_i,p.err_z , s.z, s.zerr into mydb.MyTable_# from thingIndex AS t  JOIN detectionindex AS d ON t.thingid = d.thingid JOIN specobj  AS s ON t.objid = s.bestobjid  JOIN photoobjall  AS p ON p.objid = d.objid  where p.ra=#	 ORDER BY t.thingid ASC
